longName: iShares Trust - iShares U.S. Consumer Services ETF
longBusinessSummary: iShares Trust - iShares U.S. Consumer Services ETF is an exchange traded fund launched by BlackRock, Inc. The fund is managed by BlackRock Fund Advisors. It invests in public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across consumer discretionary, consumer services sectors. The fund invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalization. It seeks to track the performance of the Dow Jones U.S. Consumer Services Capped Index , by using representative sampling technique. iShares Trust - iShares U.S. Consumer Services ETF was formed on June 12, 2000 and is domiciled in the United States.
